<ab>Wygeleis <expan>Schenk<ex>en</ex></expan> zu Geyrn</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Wygeleis, als ir uns
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>s</expan>
<expan>armman<ex>n</ex>s</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, der bey uns zu rechtent hat etc., also
                                <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        schöpfen befolhen, dem <add>ewern</add> slewnigs rechten zu helffen
                                <expan>ungev<ex>er</ex>lichen</expan>. Denn als ir uns
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>gnedigist<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> des <expan>römisch<ex>en</ex></expan> etc.
                        künigs <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, davon <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        wir zu disen <expan>zeit<ex>en</ex></expan> niht
                                <expan>treffenlich<ex>er</ex></expan> meͣre, denn die nehst
                                <expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>, die wir gehabt
                                <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>, do was sein
                            <expan>künigl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gnade dennoch zu Prünn. Und wo wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
